INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_0r3t7cj3av_posts` VALUES (374, 1, '2014-09-15 15:17:42', '2014-09-15 15:17:42', '<div class="container-sp hidden-xs" style="background-image: url(\'http://lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/lm_offices_july2014_08.jpg\');"></div>\r\n<div class="container-sp-height hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<h1 class="blue">The Lifematters Difference</h1>\r\nWe understand how vital your family and loved ones are to you. After all, each of us is a son or daughter, spouse, parent, sister, brother or friend.\r\n\r\nWe are here because we have a passionate commitment to deliver the quality of care that we would expect and require for our own family and loved ones.\r\n\r\nLifematters’ mission is to dramatically improve the lives of our clients by helping them manage their personal and health care needs in the comfort and privacy of their own homes.\r\n\r\nScroll down to learn about our differentiators and what makes us the best choice for your home care needs.\r\n<table id="lmd" class="table table-striped" style="min-height: 352px;">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th width="50%">Credential</th>\r\n<th width="50%">Lifematters</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="50%">Employed Caregivers with insurance, workers’ compensation</td>\r\n<td width="50%">✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dedicated Client Service, Clinical Team, Management &amp; Support</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Local Presence &amp; Independently Owned</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Awards</td>\r\n<td>Inc 500, Gazette, Bethesda Magazine, SmartCEO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Training</td>\r\n<td>Lifematters University</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Type of care</td>\r\n<td>Home Care, Skilled Nursing, FlexCare</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Specialization of care</td>\r\n<td>Alzheimer’s, ALS, Dementia, Diabetes and more</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td># of caregivers</td>\r\n<td>1,000+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>RN assessment</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Caregiver vetting process</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Customized matching</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>FlexCare presence</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Care / task tracking system</td>\r\n<td>Proprietary telephony system</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="hidden-xs">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="50%">\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="qualityandexpertise" class="anchor" title="Quality and Expertise"></a>Quality and Expertise</h2>\r\nWe have the most highly qualified, experienced, and trained caregivers and care managers in the business. Our employees are thoroughly screened and meticulously selected to ensure they deliver on our industry-leading standards of quality and care. 100% of our caregivers hold Certified Nursing Assistant certificates or equivalent education and experience. And because we spend more time and energy on rigorous training for all of our CNAs, GNAs, and other staff, we’re able to hire and retain the best caregivers in the industry.</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="completecareservices" class="anchor" title="Complete Care Services"></a>Complete Care Services</h2>\r\nLifematters is one of a few home care companies that provides full-service capabilities in home care. From home care, to skilled nursing services, to highly-specialized care for chronic diseases such as dementia, Alzheimer’s, Diabetes, ALS, and Parkinson’s. Whatever your home care needs are, Lifematters can provide the solution.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Work" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn more about Our Training Processes<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Can Help" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about How We Can Help<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="choice" class="anchor" title="Choice"></a>Choice</h2>\r\nNo one else gives you the ability to choose the exact caregiver you want from a group of the most qualified caregivers in the business, based on your unique care profile and requirements.</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="supportandreliability" class="anchor" title="24x7x365 Support and Reliability"></a>24x7x365 Support and Reliability</h2>\r\nWe know how essential good communication is to good care. Whether you have an emergency, need to schedule a caregiver immediately, change your existing schedule, or get answers to your questions, we are here 24x7, 365 days a year.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Work" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about our Matching Process<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="Contact Us" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/contact-us/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Contact Us Today<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="technologyandinnovation" class="anchor" title="Technology and Innovation"></a>Technology and Innovation</h2>\r\nWe use and provide the latest technologies to help guarantee our caregivers’ accountability. From ensuring on-time arrivals and end-of-shift departures through our automated telecom systems, to having the ability to provide you with state-of-the-art health and safety monitoring devices, Lifematters offers cutting edge technologies that ease and improve living.</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<div class="visible-xs-block">\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="qualityandexpertise" class="anchor" title="Quality and Expertise"></a>Quality and Expertise</h2>\r\nWe have the most highly qualified, experienced, and trained caregivers and care managers in the business. Our employees are thoroughly screened and meticulously selected to ensure they deliver on our industry-leading standards of quality and care. 100% of our caregivers hold Certified Nursing Assistant certificates or equivalent education and experience. And because we spend more time and energy on rigorous training for all of our CNAs, GNAs, and other staff, we’re able to hire and retain the best caregivers in the industry.<a title="How We Work" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn more about Our Training Processes<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="completecareservices" class="anchor" title="Complete Care Services"></a>Complete Care Services</h2>\r\nLifematters is one of a few home care companies that provides full-service capabilities in home care. From home care, to skilled nursing services, to highly-specialized care for chronic diseases such as dementia, Alzheimer’s, Diabetes, ALS, and Parkinson’s. Whatever your home care needs are, Lifematters can provide the solution.<a title="How We Can Help" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about How We Can Help<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="choice" class="anchor" title="Choice"></a>Choice</h2>\r\nNo one else gives you the ability to choose the exact caregiver you want from a group of the most qualified caregivers in the business, based on your unique care profile and requirements.<a title="How We Work" href="http://lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about our Matching Process<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="supportandreliability" class="anchor" title="24x7x365 Support and Reliability"></a>24x7x365 Support and Reliability</h2>\r\nWe know how essential good communication is to good care. Whether you have an emergency, need to schedule a caregiver immediately, change your existing schedule, or get answers t