DF once you\'ve filled it out completely, save the document to your computer, then open it in Adobe Reader (PDF Software).</span> <strong><a title="Download Adobe Reader FREE" href="http://get.adobe.com/reader" target="_blank">Download it here</a></strong> for free if needed.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Using your printer</strong>, print out the document, and fill out by hand with a dark inked pen.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Submit your application by either:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Clicking the "Submit" or "Submit form" buttons</strong> within the PDF (Must use Adobe Reader for buttons to function)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Emailing your completed application</strong> as an attachment to <a href="mailto:apply@lifemattersusa.com" target="_blank">apply@lifemattersusa.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Faxing your application</strong> to (301) 652-7215</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li> Your application will be then reviewed by our Human Resources team, and we will contact you if a match that complements your skills, experiences, and indicated availability is found amongst our current hiring needs.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-body"><button class="btn btn-link reqs important" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#joinModal"><img class="pull-left" src="http://lifematters.digitalhealthstrategies.com/wp-content/themes/LifeMattersUSA.com/img/icons/important_blk.svg" alt="" width="30px" height="auto" />Important: CNA, GNA, LPN and RN applicants click here to read important application requirements.</button></div>\r\n</div>', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-15 15:24:27', '2014-09-15 15:24:27', '', 92, 'http://lifemattersusa.com/blog/92-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
