INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_0r3t7cj3av_posts` VALUES (450, 1, '2014-09-17 05:38:19', '2014-09-17 05:38:19', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row home_vid">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 bdy">\r\n<h3 class="hdr blue"><span class="orng">LifeMatters:</span> Delivering Peace of Mind</h3>\r\nOver the past decade, Lifematters has become the first choice for home care in Maryland, Washington, D.C. and Northern Virginia. We work with our clients to create fully customized care plans staffed by our team of highly trained and skilled caregivers that deliver on a full range of in-home services.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">\r\n<div id="vidthumb" class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"><img class="img-responsive aligncenter" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/lifematters_video_titlecard.jpg" alt="" width="661" height="371" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container-fluid quote green_bg green_tx">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">We provide consistent, top quality service for both customers and employees through a unique combination of compassionate care, reliability and professionalism. That\'s the Lifematters Difference.\r\n<a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/thelifemattersdifference"><button class="hrz_btnB wht_bg">Learn More About What Sets Us Apart<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container site-content">\r\n<div class="row home_sp howwecanhelp">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 hdr">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle blue_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/hands.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/hands.png\'" alt="Icon" width="100" height="100" />\r\n<h1 class="blue">How We Can Help</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr class="blue_bg" />\r\n\r\nIt’s not just about being at home. It\'s about living as well as possible at home. Lifematters offers a full range of in-home services ranging from personal companionship to medical care, including general home management, nutrition and meals, mobility activities, and skilled nursing care. Whatever your needs, Lifematters will work with you to create and deliver on the right care plan. You will be supported by a full care team consisting of your caregiver and dedicated team members from client services, clinical care and corporate leadership. <a class="readmore" title="How We Can Help" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp/">Read more</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl" style="margin-left: 11%;">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle green_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/homecare.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/homecare.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Home Care</h3>\r\nStay safe, well and happy in the comfort of your home with the support of our certified caregivers.     <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp#homecare"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle red_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/skillednursing.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/skillednursing.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Skilled Nursing</h3>\r\nGet the clinical care you require from our team of RNs and LPNs. <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp#skillednursing"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle orng_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/diseasespecialties.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/diseasespecialties.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Disease Specialties</h3>\r\nReceive highly trained and specialized care for your disease or chronic condition.   <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp#diseasespecialties"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle gold_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/flexcare.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/flexcare.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Flexcare</h3>\r\nMaintain an independent lifestyle at your continuing care residential community with our on-site services. <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp#flexcare"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container-fluid quote gold_bg gold_tx">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">"I knew the decision I was about to make for my family was huge, and you made it easy. I want to commend Lifematters and the staff you have hired and trained for making our experience a smooth one." - Julie <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/testimonials"><button class="hrz_btnB wht_bg">Read Our Testimonials<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container site-content">\r\n<div class="row home_sp">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 hdr">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle blue_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/gears.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/gears.png\'" alt="Icon" width="100" height="100" />\r\n<h1 class="blue">How We Work</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr class="blue_bg" />\r\n\r\nFinding the right care for you or a loved one can be overwhelming. But we are here to help you navigate this difficult process every step of the way. Our care management experts and client services team have spent decades working with families in need of home care. With the <em>Lifematters Care Plan Process</em>, you will get the necessary answers and solutions, whether you simply want guidance through the home care maze or urgently need a caregiver at your home today. <a class="readmore" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework">Read more</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl" style="margin-left: 21%;">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle gold_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwematch.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwematch.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>How We Match</h3>\r\nWith our proprietary matching process, you receive a customized care plan and caregiver based on your specific needs, requests and situation. <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework#howwematch"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle red_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwetrain.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwetrain.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>How We Train</h3>\r\nOur employees must complete our extensive Lifematters University training curriculum that sets the standard for the industry. <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework#howwetrain"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle orng_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwehire.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/howwehire.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>How We Hire</h3>\r\nWe hire only the top 20% of applicants who pass our rigorous vetting, interviewing and testing qualifications. <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework#howwehire"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container-fluid quote teal_bg teal_tx">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">“Carl was not just Dad\'s caregiver. He was his friend. He gently pushed him to do more than he thought he could do. Carl is our angel.” - Mrs. D <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/testimonials"><button class="hrz_btnB wht_bg">Read Our Testimonials<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container site-content">\r\n<div class="row home_sp" style="padding-bottom: 10px;">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 hdr">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle blue_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/whoweare.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/whoweare.png\'" alt="Icon" width="100" height="100" />\r\n<h1 class="blue">Who We Are</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr class="blue_bg" />\r\n\r\nOur people are our most valuable asset. The Lifematters team, all of whom live in the Washington DC metropolitan area, bring decades of proven experience in home care. We have more than 1,000 employees, but maintain a close-knit and familial environment. Each Lifematters employee has a unique background and skill set that adds value to our collective whole.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin-bottom: 30px;"><a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/whoweare"><button class="hrz_btnA green_bg wht" style="padding-left: 4em; padding-right: 4em;">Meet Our Team</button></a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="container-fluid quote red_bg red_tx">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">“Your CNAs and LPNs were a very caring and professional team, assisting our family under crisis conditions with vigilance.” - Betty <a class="readmore" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/testimonials"><button class="hrz_btnB wht_bg">Read Our Testimonials <span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container site-content">\r\n<div class="row home_sp our_story">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 hdr">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle blue_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/ourstory.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/ourstory.png\'" alt="Icon" width="100" height="100" />\r\n<h1 class="blue">Our Story</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr class="blue_bg" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle green_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/ourhistory.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/ourhistory.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Our History</h3>\r\nRead about our local origins and how we\'ve grown to become the largest employer based home care company in the DC region.     <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/ourstory#ourhistory"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle red_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/affiliations.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/affiliations.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Affiliations</h3>\r\nLearn about our network of non-profit alliances and how they add to the Lifematters Difference.     <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/ourstory#ourpartnersandaffiliates"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle gold_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/locations.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/locations.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Locations</h3>\r\nGet in touch and find our corporate locations across DC, Maryland and Virginia.<a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/contactus#officelocations"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle teal_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/jobs.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/jobs.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Join Our Team</h3>\r\nLearn about why Lifematters is a great place to work and search available positions.       <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/joinourteam"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vrtpnl">\r\n\r\n<img class="hdricon img-circle orng_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/blog.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/blog.png\'" alt="Icon" width="86" height="86" />\r\n<h3>Blog</h3>\r\nKeep up with the latest news, information and resources from the world of home care.       <a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog"><button class="hrz_btnA blue_bg">Read More</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container awards">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<h3>Awards</h3>\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img style="max-width: 65%;" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/awards_inc500.jpg" alt="" width="100%" height="auto" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img style="max-width: 55%;" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/awards_bethesda.jpg" alt="" width="100%" height="auto" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img style="max-width: 90%; margin-top: 2em;" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/awards_future50.jpg" alt="" width="100%" height="auto" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img style="max-width: 55%;" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/awards_gazette.jpg" alt="" width="100%" height="auto" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-17 05:38:19', '2014-09-17 05:38:19', '', 88, 'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_0r3t7cj3av_posts` VALUES (468, 1, '2014-09-17 08:04:58', '2014-09-17 08:04:58', '<div class="container-sp hidden-xs" style="background-image: url(\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/IMG_0319.jpg\');"></div>\r\n<div class="container-sp-height hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<h1 class="blue">The Lifematters Difference</h1>\r\nWe understand how vital your family and loved ones are to you. After all, each of us is a son or daughter, spouse, parent, sister, brother or friend.\r\n\r\nWe are here because we have a passionate commitment to deliver the quality of care that we would expect and require for our own family and loved ones.\r\n\r\nLifematters’ mission is to dramatically improve the lives of our clients by helping them manage their personal and health care needs in the comfort and privacy of their own homes.\r\n\r\nScroll down to learn about our differentiators and what makes us the best choice for your home care needs.\r\n<table id="lmd" class="table table-striped" style="min-height: 352px;">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th width="50%">Credential</th>\r\n<th width="50%">Lifematters</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="50%">Employed Caregivers with insurance, workers’ compensation</td>\r\n<td width="50%">✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dedicated Client Service, Clinical Team, Management &amp; Support</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Local Presence &amp; Independently Owned</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Awards</td>\r\n<td>Inc 500, Gazette, Bethesda Magazine, SmartCEO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Training</td>\r\n<td>Lifematters University</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Type of care</td>\r\n<td>Home Care, Skilled Nursing, FlexCare</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Specialization of care</td>\r\n<td>Alzheimer’s, ALS, Dementia, Diabetes and more</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td># of caregivers</td>\r\n<td>1,000+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>RN assessment</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Caregiver vetting process</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Customized matching</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>FlexCare presence</td>\r\n<td>✓</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Care / task tracking system</td>\r\n<td>Proprietary telephony system</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="hidden-xs">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="50%">\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="qualityandexpertise" class="anchor" title="Quality and Expertise"></a>Quality and Expertise</h2>\r\nWe have the most highly qualified, experienced, and trained caregivers and care managers in the business. Our employees are thoroughly screened and meticulously selected to ensure they deliver on our industry-leading standards of quality and care. 100% of our caregivers hold Certified Nursing Assistant certificates or equivalent education and experience. And because we spend more time and energy on rigorous training for all of our CNAs, GNAs, and other staff, we’re able to hire and retain the best caregivers in the industry.</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="completecareservices" class="anchor" title="Complete Care Services"></a>Complete Care Services</h2>\r\nLifematters is one of a few home care companies that provides full-service capabilities in home care. From home care, to skilled nursing services, to highly-specialized care for chronic diseases such as dementia, Alzheimer’s, Diabetes, ALS, and Parkinson’s. Whatever your home care needs are, Lifematters can provide the solution.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Work" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn more about Our Training Processes<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Can Help" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about How We Can Help<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="choice" class="anchor" title="Choice"></a>Choice</h2>\r\nNo one else gives you the ability to choose the exact caregiver you want from a group of the most qualified caregivers in the business, based on your unique care profile and requirements.</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="supportandreliability" class="anchor" title="24x7x365 Support and Reliability"></a>24x7x365 Support and Reliability</h2>\r\nWe know how essential good communication is to good care. Whether you have an emergency, need to schedule a caregiver immediately, change your existing schedule, or get answers to your questions, we are here 24x7, 365 days a year.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="How We Work" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about our Matching Process<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n<td style="padding-top: 20px;"><a title="Contact Us" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/contactus/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Contact Us Today<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="technologyandinnovation" class="anchor" title="Technology and Innovation"></a>Technology and Innovation</h2>\r\nWe use and provide the latest technologies to help guarantee our caregivers’ accountability. From ensuring on-time arrivals and end-of-shift departures through our automated telecom systems, to having the ability to provide you with state-of-the-art health and safety monitoring devices, Lifematters offers cutting edge technologies that ease and improve living.</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<div class="visible-xs-block">\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="qualityandexpertise" class="anchor" title="Quality and Expertise"></a>Quality and Expertise</h2>\r\nWe have the most highly qualified, experienced, and trained caregivers and care managers in the business. Our employees are thoroughly screened and meticulously selected to ensure they deliver on our industry-leading standards of quality and care. 100% of our caregivers hold Certified Nursing Assistant certificates or equivalent education and experience. And because we spend more time and energy on rigorous training for all of our CNAs, GNAs, and other staff, we’re able to hire and retain the best caregivers in the industry.<a title="How We Work" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn more about Our Training Processes<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="completecareservices" class="anchor" title="Complete Care Services"></a>Complete Care Services</h2>\r\nLifematters is one of a few home care companies that provides full-service capabilities in home care. From home care, to skilled nursing services, to highly-specialized care for chronic diseases such as dementia, Alzheimer’s, Diabetes, ALS, and Parkinson’s. Whatever your home care needs are, Lifematters can provide the solution.<a title="How We Can Help" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwecanhelp/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about How We Can Help<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="choice" class="anchor" title="Choice"></a>Choice</h2>\r\nNo one else gives you the ability to choose the exact caregiver you want from a group of the most qualified caregivers in the business, based on your unique care profile and requirements.<a title="How We Work" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/howwework"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn More about our Matching Process<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="supportandreliability" class="anchor" title="24x7x365 Support and Reliability"></a>24x7x365 Support and Reliability</h2>\r\nWe know how essential good communication is to good care. Whether you have an emergency, need to schedule a caregiver immediately, change your existing schedule, or get answers to your questions, we are here 24x7, 365 days a year.<a title="Contact Us" href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/contactus"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Contact Us Today<span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="blue"><a id="technologyandinnovation" class="anchor" title="Technology and Innovation"></a>Technology and Innovation</h2>\r\nWe use and provide the latest technologies to help guarantee our caregivers’ accountability. From ensuring on-time arrivals and end-of-shift departures through our automated telecom systems, to having the ability to provide you with state-of-the-art health and safety monitoring devices, Lifematters offers cutting edge technologies that ease and improve living.</div>', 'The Lifematters Difference', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '109-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-17 08:04:58', '2014-09-17 08:04:58', '', 109, 'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog/109-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
