ogo">\r\n<div class="thumb" style="background-image: url(\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/dhs.png\');"></div>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n\r\nDigital Health Strategies\r\n<a href="http://digitalhealthstrategies.com" target="_blank"><h3>digitalhealthstrategies.com</h3></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-2 affllogo">\r\n<div class="thumb" style="background-image: url(\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/homecareplus.png\');"></div>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n\r\nHomecare Plus\r\n<a href="http://homecareplus.org" target="_blank"><h3>homecareplus.org</h3></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row strategicpartners">\r\n<div class="col-sm-2 affllogo">\r\n<div class="thumb" style="background-image: url(\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/houseworks.png\');"></div>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n\r\nHouse-Works\r\n<a href="http://house-works.com" target="_blank"><h3>house-works.com</h3></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Our Corporate Social Responsibility:</h3>\r\n<h4>We support a variety of non-profit organizations throughout the region and across the country.</h4>\r\n<ul class="section_end">\r\n	<li>ALS Association of DC/MD/VA – <a href="http://alsinfo.org" target="_blank">alsinfo.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Alzheimer’s Association – <a href="http://alz.org" target="_blank">alz.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Anti-Defamation League – <a href="http://adl.org" target="_blank">adl.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Kid Save International – <a href="http://kidsave.org" target="_blank">kidsave.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Holy Cross Hospital Foundation – <a href="http://holycrosshealth.org/foundation" target="_blank">holycrosshealth.org/foundation</a></li>\r\n	<li>Iona Senior Services of Washington – <a href="http://iona.org" target="_blank">iona.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Jesuit Community at Georgetown University – <a href="http://jesuits.georgetown.edu" target="_blank">jesuits.georgetown.edu</a></li>\r\n	<li>Leukemia &amp; Lymphoma Society – <a href="http://lls.org" target="_blank">lls.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Northwest Neighbors Village, Washington, DC – <a href="http://nwnv.org" target="_blank">nwnv.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Wounded Warriors Project – <a href="http://woundedwarriorproject.org" target="_blank">woundedwarriorproject.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Arlington Free Clinic – <a href="http://arlingtonfreeclinic.org" target="_blank">arlingtonfreeclinic.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Becky’s Fund – <a href="http://beckysfund.org" target="_blank">beckysfund.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Inova Health System Foundation – <a href="http://foundation.inova.org" target="_blank">foundation.inova.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Inova Loudoun Hospital - <a href="inova.org/patient-and-visitor-information/facilities/inova-loudoun-hospital">inova.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Arts for the Ages (to benefit the Alzheimer’s Association) - <a href="http://fineartamerica.com/events/art-for-the-ages.html">fineartamerica.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>Chevy Chase at Home – <a href="http://www.chevychaseathome.org">chevychaseathome.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>MedStar National Rehabilitation Hospital - <a href="https://www.medstarhealth.org/nrh/Pages/default.aspx">medstarhealth.org</a></li>\r\n	<li>Guide to Retirement Living - <a href="http://www.retirement-living.com/">retirement-living.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>Family Pass - <a href="http://familypassfairfax.org/" target="_blank">familypass.org</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '105-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-17 08:11:35', '2014-09-17 08:11:35', '', 105, 'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog/105-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_0r3t7cj3av_posts` VALUES (473, 1, '2014-09-17 08:14:28', '2014-09-17 08:14:28', '<div class="container-sp hidden-xs" style="background-image: url(\'http://lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/lm_offices_july2014_30.jpg\');"></div>\r\n<div class="container-sp-height hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<h1 class="blue">Join Our Team</h1>\r\nWe are proud of our commitment to every member of our team. We have cultivated a culture of respect and collaboration. As a result, the compassionate, professional and reliable home care our Lifematters’ team provides is the best in the industry. We hire the right individuals and give them the tools and resources they need to ensure they deliver unsurpassed care for our clients. Here are just a few of the reasons why Lifematters is a great place to work:\r\n<table class="hidden-xs">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="50%">\r\n<h2 class="blue">Career Management and Development</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Competitive salaries and great benefits</li>\r\n	<li>Annual goal setting and reviews</li>\r\n	<li>Caregiver roundtables</li>\r\n	<li>Merit based bonuses</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="50%">\r\n<h2 class="blue">Training</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lifematters University curriculum including specialized care</li>\r\n	<li>Ongoing courses for certification</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue">Team Based Working Environment</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Full support team made up of client services, clinical team and corporate leadership</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate offices across DC, MD and VA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 class="blue">Long Tenure, Low Turnover</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The majority of our staff has been with Lifematters for multiple years</li>\r\n	<li>Our average caregiver tenure is 3 years</li>\r\n	<li>Our average corporate staff tenure is 5 years</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<ul class="visible-xs-block">\r\n	<h2 class="blue">Career Management and Development</h2>\r\n	<li>Competitive salaries and great benefits</li>\r\n	<li>Annual goal setting and reviews</li>\r\n	<li>Caregiver roundtables</li>\r\n	<li>Merit based bonuses</li>\r\n	<h2 class="blue">Training</h2>\r\n	<li>Lifematters University curriculum including specialized care</li>\r\n	<li>Ongoing courses for certification</li>\r\n	<h2 class="blue">Team Based Working Environment</h2>\r\n	<li>Full support team made up of client services, clinical team and corporate leadership</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate offices across DC, MD and VA</li>\r\n	<h2 class="blue">Long Tenure, Low Turnover</h2>\r\n	<li>The majority of our staff has been with Lifematters for multiple years</li>\r\n	<li>Our average caregiver tenure is 3 years</li>\r\n	<li>Our average corporate staff tenure is 5 years</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="container-sp hidden-xs" style="background-image: url(\'http://lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/lm_offices_july2014_28.jpg\');"></div>\r\n<div class="container-sp-height hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<h1 class="blue"><a id="openpositions" class="anchor"></a>Open Positions</h1>\r\n<h3>We hire for the following areas. See below for current openings.</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nursing (registered and licensed practical nurses)</li>\r\n	<li>Social work</li>\r\n	<li>Home care (caregivers)</li>\r\n	<li>Business development</li>\r\n	<li>Client services</li>\r\n	<li>Care coordinators</li>\r\n	<li>Accounting</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>How to Apply</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>View each <strong>Current Openings</strong> listing below</li>\r\n	<li>Click below to start the application process. A document (.pdf) will automatically download, or may just open in a browser window. </span></li>\r\n	<li>Fill out application completely by either:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Using your computer</strong>, click each field and fill out corresponding information. <span style="color: #222222;">If you are having issues submitting your PDF once you\'ve filled it out completely, save the document to your computer, then open it in Adobe Reader (PDF Software).</span> <strong><a title="Download Adobe Reader FREE" href="http://get.adobe.com/reader" target="_blank">Download it here</a></strong> for free if needed.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Using your printer</strong>, print out the document, and fill out by hand with a dark inked pen.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Submit your application by either:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Clicking the "Submit" or "Submit form" buttons</strong> within the PDF (Must use Adobe Reader for buttons to function)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Emailing your completed application</strong> as an attachment to <a href="mailto:apply@lifemattersusa.com" target="_blank">apply@lifemattersusa.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Faxing your application</strong> to (301) 652-7215</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li> Your application will be then reviewed by our Human Resources team, and we will contact you if a match that complements your skills, experiences, and indicated availability is found amongst our current hiring needs.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-body"><button class="btn btn-link reqs important" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#joinModal"><img class="pull-left" src="http://lifematters.digitalhealthstrategies.com/wp-content/themes/LifeMattersUSA.com/img/icons/important_blk.svg" alt="" width="30px" height="auto" />Important: CNA, GNA, LPN and RN applicants click here to read important application requirements.</button></div>\r\n</div>', 'Join Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '103-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-17 08:14:28', '2014-09-17 08:14:28', '', 103, 'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog/103-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
