t is our people, so our team is our most important asset. Each of our caregivers undergoes hours of training developed by Lifematters University – the most comprehensive caregiver training program in the country.\r\n\r\n<img id="lmulogo" class="center-block" style="padding: 2em 1em 1em;" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/lm_university_logo.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/lm_university_logo.png\'" alt="" width="70%" height="auto" />\r\n\r\nOur Training Program offers an extensive array of courses that include:\r\n<table class="table table-striped">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="40%"><strong>Basic Training</strong></td>\r\n<td width="60%">Personal Care, Hygiene, Mobility and Transferring, Nutrition, and Home Management</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Health Training</strong></td>\r\n<td>Comprehensive Competency Assessment by Staff RNs, Wound Care, Medication Assistance, CPR, UTI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Disease Training</strong></td>\r\n<td>Alzheimers, Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS), Parkinsons, Multiple Sclerosis, and Diabetes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Nutrition</strong></td>\r\n<td>Diabetic, Gluten Free, Low Sodium, Vegetarian, Kosher and Halal Diet Requirements</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cultural Training </strong></td>\r\n<td>Communications and Interpersonal Training, Satisfaction, Hospitality</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>At-Risk Training</strong></td>\r\n<td>Recognizing Depression</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Safety Training</strong></td>\r\n<td>Oxygen Safety</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div  class="container-sp hidden-xs" style="background-image: url(\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/lm_offices_july2014_09.jpg\'); background-position: center -30px;"></div>\r\n<div  class="container-sp-height hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<h1 class="blue"><a id="howwehire" class="anchor"></a>How We Hire</h1>\r\nYou can take comfort in knowing that all Lifematters employees have completed our rigorous hiring process that includes proprietary interviewing and testing protocols. 100% of Lifematters caregivers hold Certified Nursing Assistant Certificates or equivalent education and experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="col-xs-4" style="text-align: center;"><img class="img-circle gold_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/nursingassistantseal.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/nursingassistantseal.png\'" alt="" width="125" height="125" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-xs-4" style="text-align: center;"><img class="img-circle blue_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/registerednurseseal.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/registerednurseseal.png\'" alt="" width="125" height="125" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-xs-4" style="text-align: center;"><img class="img-circle teal_bg" src="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/licensedpracticalnurse.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src=\'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/img/icons/licensedpracticalnurse.png\'" alt="" width="125" height="125" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEvery caregiver that works at Lifematters is an employee, not a sub-contractor. We vet our caregivers against multiple requirements before being hired.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enhanced security background investigation</li>\r\n	<li>Criminal history search</li>\r\n	<li>Social Security Number trace</li>\r\n	<li>Motor vehicle report</li>\r\n	<li>Verification of CNA training and certification</li>\r\n	<li>Confirmation of U.S. employment eligibility</li>\r\n	<li>Personal and professional references</li>\r\n	<li>Multiple rounds of in-person panel interviews with HR, clinical, client services and corporate leadership team</li>\r\n	<li>Lifematters fees cover all employment wages and taxes</li>\r\n	<li>Lifematters employees have workers compensation and liability insurance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.lifemattersusa.com/joinourteam/"><button class="hrz_btnB ltgrey_bg">Learn more about the Lifematters Team Culture and see a list of Open Positions <span class="arw_sym">▶</span></button></a>', 'How We Work', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '101-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-18 06:09:29', '2014-09-18 06:09:29', '', 101, 'http://www.lifemattersusa.com/blog/101-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
